abstract: >
  An AI-powered framework for automated knowledge-level classification
  and summarization of educational videos using OpenAI Whisper,
  BERT, and Longformer Encoder Decoder (LED). The framework
  generates timestamped transcripts, classifies educational content
  into cognitive knowledge levels, and produces concise summaries
  to enhance learning and educational analytics.

